From: Peter Chen <peter.chen@freescale.com>
Date: Mon, 19 Aug 2013 12:42:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0232/1072] ENGR00275634: ARM: imx_v6_v7_defconfig: Add some
 USB configurations

git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git imx_3.10.17_1.0.0_beta
commit 39a681f4b30c79e9b701c8701b3f79013a0e6670

- Enable USB gadget function
- Enable USB Audio and Camera functions
- Disable CONFIG_USB_EHCI_MXC to avoid confusion due to we
only use chipidea driver as USB driver for this BSP

Signed-off-by: Peter Chen <peter.chen@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Hongbo Zhong <hongbo.zhong@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig |   10 +++++++++-
 1 files changed, 9 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
index d1853ad..efef3d7 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
@@ -181,6 +181,8 @@ CONFIG_REGULATOR_MC13892=y
 CONFIG_REGULATOR_PFUZE100=y
 CONFIG_MEDIA_SUPPORT=y
 CONFIG_MEDIA_CAMERA_SUPPORT=y
+CONFIG_MEDIA_USB_SUPPORT=y
+CONFIG_USB_VIDEO_CLASS=m
 CONFIG_V4L_PLATFORM_DRIVERS=y
 CONFIG_VIDEO_MXC_OUTPUT=y
 CONFIG_VIDEO_MXC_IPU_OUTPUT=y
@@ -207,6 +209,7 @@ CONFIG_FONT_8x16=y
 CONFIG_LOGO=y
 CONFIG_SOUND=y
 CONFIG_SND=y
+CONFIG_SND_USB_AUDIO=m
 CONFIG_SND_SOC=y
 CONFIG_SND_IMX_SOC=y
 CONFIG_SND_SOC_PHYCORE_AC97=y
@@ -217,12 +220,17 @@ CONFIG_SND_SOC_IMX_SGTL5000=y
 CONFIG_SND_SOC_IMX_MC13783=y
 CONFIG_USB=y
 CONFIG_USB_EHCI_HCD=y
-CONFIG_USB_EHCI_MXC=y
